item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossy)】MP3 - SOPHIE - TRANSNATION (2021 SCRAPPED ALBUM)
item.description:
TRANSNATION (2020 SCRAPPED ALBUM)
Concept of SOPHIE's scrapped album TRANSNATION based around a tracklist obtained from a 2020 email leak. Tracklist in said email was very rough and loosely concepted, but provided a vision to fulfill nonetheless.

ALTERNATIVE COVER INCLUDED - EVERYONE IS ENCOURAGED TO SHARE THEIR OWN

Tracklist
1. Take Me To Dubai
2. New York's Buring Down
3. Burn Rubber
4. Sunscreen
5. Flybitch
6. Don't Make Me Wait
7. Lock It Up
8. In The Rain
9. Plunging Asymptote
10. Rawwww
11. Reason Why
12. Europe for the Summer
13. WGFU?*
14. Do U Wanna Be Alive (Remake)
15. Love Me Off Earth
16. Exhilarate
17. My Forever
18. Transnation

BONUS
19.Taxi*
20. Do U Wanna Be Alive (Version II)
21. Transnation (Demo)

*Tracklist has both songs filling the same spot, suggesting that spot was up for debate, so both were included. Use at your own discretion.

File names left as found, only edit is TMTD was given a volume bump
